### Registrar novo cliente
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/inscription
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nom": "João Silva",
  "email": "joao@example.com",
  "telephone": "123456789",
  "motDePasse": "senha123456"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/connexion
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao@example.com",
  "motDePasse": "senha123456"
}